regular-body:
Is futile to argue. Nod. Get treat. Only certainty in life: when icy jaws of death come, you will not have had enough treats. Nod. Get treat. – Order of the Stick #1037

All deaths horrible. Also inevitable. Nod. Get treat. – Order of the Stick #1037

Should always expect head rub. Safer that way. […] See? Specter of noogie hangs like shroud over us all. – Order of the Stick #1038
regular-title: Brilliant things from my new favourite OOTS character
